com.tsgrp.migration.event

Class ERoomSimpleDataLoaderListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.event.ERoomSimpleDataLoaderListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourceEndExportNodeEventListener, TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener, TargetEndImportSubNodeEventListener

    public class ERoomSimpleDataLoaderListener
extends AbstractListener
implements SourceEndExportNodeEventListener, TargetBeginImportNodeEventListener, TargetEndImportSubNodeEventListener
    Given a Node created from a single row in eRoom's Objects table, clean up key properties and determine the folder structure for the current document.

    Node Attributes Written

    • eroom_filename - hex-prefixed, URLencoded filename as stored on underlying filestore
    • om_folder - folder to write file to
    • om_name - pretty filename: no hex prefix, URL decoded if necessary
